OL,3,CTwin brother of teen killed in
OL,4,CCoventry stabbing says 'you'll be
OL,5,Cgreatly missed'
OL,7,FThe twin brother of a teenager who
OL,8,Fdied after being stabbed in Coventry
OL,9,Fsays the family will "never be the
OL,10,Fsame" and that he will be "greatly
OL,11,Fmissed".
OL,13,FMichael Ababio suffered a stab wound
OL,14,Fduring disorder outside Foleshill
OL,15,FLibrary on Broad Street at around
OL,16,F9.40pm. West Midlands Police say the
OL,17,F18-year-old was pronounced dead on
OL,18,FMonday, February 23.
OL,20,FMichael's twin brother has paid
OL,21,Ftribute on behalf of his family.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772012404
OL,3,CTwin brother of teen killed in
OL,4,CCoventry stabbing says 'you'll be
OL,5,Cgreatly missed'
OL,7,FHe said: "Most people won't know what
OL,8,Fit is like to have a twin, but I do.
OL,9,FMichael was more than just a brother,
OL,10,Fhe was my second half.
OL,12,F"He aligned with everything that I
OL,13,Fliked. Words cannot express the pain
OL,14,Fwe are all feeling right now.
OL,16,F"You will be greatly missed. Our
OL,17,Ffamily will never be the same, but we
OL,18,Fhope you're in a better place now."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
