FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772012404
OL,3,CTwin brother of teen killed in
OL,4,CCoventry stabbing says 'you'll be
OL,5,Cgreatly missed'
OL,7,FA 19-year-old man who was also found
OL,8,Fwith stab wounds nearby was taken to
OL,9,Fhospital, where he remains today. He
OL,10,Fhas also been arrested on suspicion of
OL,11,Fmurder.
OL,13,FOfficers are also investigating a
OL,14,Fdisorder that happened on nearby
OL,15,FFoleshill Road, around 20 minutes
OL,16,Fafter the fatal attack, which the
OL,17,Fforce says it doesn't believe to be
OL,18,Fdirectly related.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772012404
OL,3,CTwin brother of teen killed in
OL,4,CCoventry stabbing says 'you'll be
OL,5,Cgreatly missed'
OL,7,FFour people have been arrested in
OL,8,Fconnection with that disorder. One has
OL,9,Fsince been charged with assault and
OL,10,Fremanded in custody. The others have
OL,11,Fbeen bailed while the investigation
OL,12,Fcontinues.
OL,14,FDet Supt Jim Munro, from our Homicide
OL,15,Fteam, said: "Michael's family have
OL,16,Fbeen left devastated by his death, and
OL,17,Four focus this evening is solely on
OL,18,Fgetting answers for them and justice
OL,19,Ffor Michael.
OL,26,@wD@MOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772012404
OL,3,CTwin brother of teen killed in
OL,4,CCoventry stabbing says 'you'll be
OL,5,Cgreatly missed'
OL,7,F"We've made good progress already by
OL,8,Fspeaking to witnesses, recovering
OL,9,FCCTV, and other enquiries, but we
OL,10,Fstill really need the public's help.
OL,12,F"If you saw what happened, or you know
OL,13,Fwhy someone may wanted to have hurt
OL,14,FMichael, please do the right thing for
OL,15,Fhis family and let us know."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@\O]
